## Description {#details}

Container class for subtarget features.

This is a constexpr reimplementation of a subset of std::bitset. It would be nice to use std::bitset directly, but it doesn&#39;t support constant initialization.

Definition at line 41 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/targetparser/subtargetfeature-h">SubtargetFeature.h</a>.
